The developed algorithms and RNA structure database are included in http://rnassac.hopto.org

The pages printed out from the website do the following functions:

REandAnnotation.jpg: Lets Regular expression matching program,  and RNA structure annotation program be downloaded;

RNASubstructureDemoFromStructureFile.jpg:  RNA substructure stored in a demo file was searched in the RNA structure database;

RNASubstructureDrawingToolForSearch.jpg: A tool that user does uses drawing the substructure  of an RNA to search in a database;

MultipleRNAComparisonStart.jpg and MultipleRNAComparisonResult.jpg: The pages in which the user selects RNAs for comparison; and in which the RNA comparison tool shows  the shared substructures by all RNA structures;

Most of the results are shown in paper 1st Proof corrections_done_1740009.pdf included in the final report, published in  Special Issue of J. of Bioinformatics and Computational Biology, World Scientific, Vol. 15, No. 6, 17400009, DOI: 10.1142/S02197200177400091. RNA Secondary Structure Graphical Rendering Library was presented in IEEE CIBCB 2018 Conference.

We published 6 papers on the project's entire research. They are listed on Publications page of webpage http://rnassac.hopto.org/index.php

